================================================================================
Bundled third-party assets
================================================================================

The MIT License above covers the source code. The following bundled audio
assets are NOT covered by it — each retains the license of its original work:

- src/main/resources/assets/imaginemorefun/sounds/ride/rail_friction.ogg
  A trimmed, re-encoded loop derived from "train_wheels_ringing_speed.wav" by
  uair01 (https://freesound.org/people/uair01/sounds/57787/).
  Licensed under CC BY 3.0: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

- src/main/resources/assets/imaginemorefun/sounds/ride/wind.ogg
  A trimmed, re-encoded loop derived from "Wind cold interior" on Mixkit
  (https://mixkit.co/free-sound-effects/wind/).
  Used under the Mixkit Sound Effects Free License:
  https://mixkit.co/license/#sfxFree
